      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Grizzly Encounter",
        "Client": "Sweet-toothed Villager",
        "Description": "What are we gonna do, Hunter?\r\nWHAT ARE WE GONNA DO!?\r\nAn Arzuros attacked the latest\r\ndelivery of honey into Kamura\r\nand now there are no sweets\u2014\r\nWHAT!? Who cares if they are OK!\r\nDid you hear me? NO SWEETS!",
        "Target": "Hunt an Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Livraison en sucre",
        "Client": "Villageois gourmand",
        "Description": "Il faut faire quelque chose, et\r\nvite ! Un Arzuros a attaqu\u00E9 la\r\nderni\u00E8re livraison de miel \u00E0\r\nKamura, c\u0027est horrible ! Pour le\r\nmarchand ? Non ! Parce que Kamura\r\na une p\u00E9nurie de sucreries\r\nmaintenant \u00E0 cause de \u00E7a !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Un incontro selvaggio",
        "Client": "Abitante goloso",
        "Description": "Cosa faremo? COSA FAREMO?! Un\r\nArzuros ha attaccato i\r\nmercanti che consegnavano il\r\nmiele a Kamura e siamo rimasti\r\nsenza dolci. COSA?! A chi\r\nimporta se stanno bene...\r\nMi hai sentito? NIENTE DOLCI!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Eine gr\u00E4uliche Begegnung",
        "Client": "Naschkatze aus dem Dorf",
        "Description": "Was sollen wir nur tun? WAS\r\nSOLLEN WIR NUR TUN?! Ein\r\nArzuros hat die frische Honig-\r\nlieferung f\u00FCr Kamura attackiert\r\nund jetzt gibt es nichts S\u00FC\u00DFes--\r\nH\u00C4?! Wen juckt der Lieferant?!\r\nH\u00F6rst du nicht? NICHTS S\u00DCSSES!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Arzuros.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "\u00BFDe qui\u00E9n es esta miel?",
        "Client": "Aldeano goloso",
        "Description": "He o\u00EDdo que un Arzuros atac\u00F3\r\nhace poco a alguien que tra\u00EDa\r\nmiel a Kamura a trav\u00E9s del\r\ntemplo \u00A1y se qued\u00F3 el bot\u00EDn!\r\nSin dulces, la vida no tiene\r\nsentido; \u00A1debes acabar con \u00E9l\r\ny salvar la ruta azucarera!",
        "Target": "Caza un Arzuros",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
